Thank you for downloading Veera Yugam Demo!

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Enable "Install from Unknown Sources" in Android Settings
   Settings > Security > Unknown Sources (enable)
2. Locate this APK file in your Downloads folder
3. Tap to install
4. Launch "Veera Yugam" from your app drawer

MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS:
- Android 8.0 (Oreo) or higher
- 4GB RAM minimum (6GB recommended)
- 2GB free storage
- Adreno 530 / Mali-G71 or better GPU

DEMO INCLUDES:
- Chola Capital City (Chapter 1)
- Character creation: Veeran
- 3 main story missions
- Basic combat system
- 5 weapon types
- Horse riding tutorial

